name: latitude-and-longitude-grid-2000-line
notes: Data available online through GeoStor at http://www.geostor.arkansas.gov. AHTD 7.5' Latitude and Longitude Lines for year end 2000 information. This file contains location information for 7.5' Latitude and Longitude Lines in the state of Arkansas. These locations were extracted from the Arkansas Highway and Transportation Department county mapping files for the year 2000.
